                                        2904
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "In this section, we describe a client- server architecture designed for bug detection that also facilitates farmer involvement through a feedback loop: subscribed farmers can send their images for inspection. Any RGB trained model can be integrated into this client- server application (briefly, app). In addition, also the UAV can use this app to autonomously fly inside the orchard to collect picture in order to augment the dataset of images, and enhance the trained ML models."
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ],
