                                    "bbox": [
                                        153,
                                        2907,
                                        1202,
                                        3102
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "This client- server app is primarily utilized by farmers and autonomous UAVs for collecting RGB images to augment the image dataset, and presently, there is no direct connection with edge- based sticky traps. Nevertheless, it is technically feasible "
                                }
